<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<LanguageData>
  
  <!-- EN: Born and raised in one of the Wolfein megacities, [PAWN_nameDef] received a quality education and grew up with hopeful dreams for the future. -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryChild_01.description>[PAWN_nameDef]出生并成长于沃芬族的大城市中，在那里接受了良好的教育，并对未来充满憧憬。</Wolfein_BackstoryChild_01.description>
  <!-- EN: Wolfein urban child -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryChild_01.title>沃芬族 城市孩子</Wolfein_BackstoryChild_01.title>
  <!-- EN: urban child -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryChild_01.titleShort>城市孩子</Wolfein_BackstoryChild_01.titleShort>
  
  <!-- EN: [PAWN_nameDef] spent [PAWN_pronoun] childhood in the countryside. Like many other rural Wolfein children, it was a time filled with joy and fulfillment. -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryChild_02.description>[PAWN_nameDef]的童年是在乡村度过的，像其他乡下的沃芬孩子一样，[PAWN_pronoun]拥有一个充实而快乐的童年。</Wolfein_BackstoryChild_02.description>
  <!-- EN: Wolfein rural child -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryChild_02.title>沃芬族 乡下孩子</Wolfein_BackstoryChild_02.title>
  <!-- EN: rural child -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryChild_02.titleShort>乡下孩子</Wolfein_BackstoryChild_02.titleShort>
  
  <!-- EN: [PAWN_nameDef]'s parents passed away in a tragic accident during her early childhood. The catastrophe left a deep, lasting scar on her heart, but it also forged a stronger, more resolute will within her. -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryChild_03.description>[PAWN_nameDef]的父母在她年幼时因一场意外事故不幸去世，这场灾难给她留下了无法抹去的伤痛，但也锤炼了她坚韧的意志。</Wolfein_BackstoryChild_03.description>
  <!-- EN: Wolfein orphan -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryChild_03.title>沃芬族 遗孤</Wolfein_BackstoryChild_03.title>
  <!-- EN: orphan -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryChild_03.titleShort>遗孤</Wolfein_BackstoryChild_03.titleShort>
  
  <!-- EN: [PAWN_nameDef]'s family wasn't well-off, so she matured early. From a young age, she often helped with household chores within her ability. In front of others, [PAWN_nameDef] always came across as especially well-behaved and considerate. -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryChild_04.description>[PAWN_nameDef]的家庭并不富裕，因此她从小就十分懂事，经常帮家里分担力所能及的家务。在外人面前，[PAWN_nameDef]也总是表现得格外乖巧懂事。</Wolfein_BackstoryChild_04.description>
  <!-- EN: Wolfein tractable child -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryChild_04.title>沃芬族 懂事的孩子</Wolfein_BackstoryChild_04.title>
  <!-- EN: tractable child -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryChild_04.titleShort>懂事的孩子</Wolfein_BackstoryChild_04.titleShort>
  
  <!-- EN: [PAWN_nameDef] was a mischievous child from an early age. Her energetic and restless nature often caused trouble for those around her. It didn’t take long before she became the ringleader among the neighborhood kids — much to the dismay of the adults. -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryChild_05.description>[PAWN_nameDef]从小就非常调皮，她活泼好动的性格常常给周围的人带来不少麻烦。很快，[PAWN_nameDef]就在小伙伴中成了孩子王，这也让大人们感到十分头疼。</Wolfein_BackstoryChild_05.description>
  <!-- EN: Wolfein naughty child -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryChild_05.title>沃芬族 淘气包</Wolfein_BackstoryChild_05.title>
  <!-- EN: naughty child -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryChild_05.titleShort>淘气包</Wolfein_BackstoryChild_05.titleShort>
  
  <!-- EN: [PAWN_nameDef] was born into an average middle-class family, and her childhood was as ordinary as that of most of her peers. Yet deep down, she longed for a future filled with a unique adventure all her own. -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryChild_06.description>[PAWN_nameDef]出生于一个普通的中产阶级家庭，她的童年和大多数同龄人一样平凡无奇。但她始终渴望着，在未来能拥有一段只属于自己的独特冒险。</Wolfein_BackstoryChild_06.description>
  <!-- EN: Wolfein ordinary child -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryChild_06.title>沃芬族 平凡的孩子</Wolfein_BackstoryChild_06.title>
  <!-- EN: ordinary child -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryChild_06.titleShort>平凡的孩子</Wolfein_BackstoryChild_06.titleShort>
  
  <!-- EN: [PAWN_nameDef]'s childhood was far from smooth—minor misfortunes seemed to follow her wherever she went. Yet, when it came to major events, she always seemed incredibly lucky, narrowly escaping trouble time and again. Even her parents couldn't quite make sense of it. -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryChild_07.description>[PAWN_nameDef]的童年并不算顺利，几乎所有倒霉的小事都能落到她头上。但奇怪的是，在面对一些重大事件时，[PAWN_nameDef]却总能逢凶化吉，格外幸运，就连她的父母也无法解释其中的原因。</Wolfein_BackstoryChild_07.description>
  <!-- EN: Wolfein unlucky child -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryChild_07.title>沃芬族 倒霉蛋</Wolfein_BackstoryChild_07.title>
  <!-- EN: unlucky child -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryChild_07.titleShort>倒霉蛋</Wolfein_BackstoryChild_07.titleShort>
  
  <!-- EN: Since childhood, [PAWN_nameDef] has been afraid of interacting with others and reluctant to engage with the outside world. She finds greater comfort and peace in solitude than in the noise of social life. -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryChild_08.description>[PAWN_nameDef]从小就害怕与人交流，也不喜欢接触外面的世界。相比喧嚣的人群，她更享受独处带来的宁静与安全感。</Wolfein_BackstoryChild_08.description>
  <!-- EN: Wolfein autistic child -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryChild_08.title>沃芬族 自闭儿童</Wolfein_BackstoryChild_08.title>
  <!-- EN: autistic child -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryChild_08.titleShort>自闭儿童</Wolfein_BackstoryChild_08.titleShort>
  
  <!-- EN: [PAWN_nameDef] is extremely timid— even the slightest noise can startle her. Her anxious and easily frightened nature has often brought complications into her daily life. -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryChild_09.description>[PAWN_nameDef]胆子极小，稍有风吹草动都会让她惊慌失措。她那敏感多疑、动辄受惊的性格，也给她的生活带来了不少困扰。</Wolfein_BackstoryChild_09.description>
  <!-- EN: Wolfein timid child -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryChild_09.title>沃芬族 胆小的孩子</Wolfein_BackstoryChild_09.title>
  <!-- EN: timid child -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryChild_09.titleShort>胆小的孩子</Wolfein_BackstoryChild_09.titleShort>
  
  <!-- EN: [PAWN_nameDef] has a deep love for the feeling of gaining new knowledge, spending nearly all her time immersed in study. Her favorite place to be is the local library near her home, where she can lose herself for hours on end. -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryChild_10.description>[PAWN_nameDef]非常热爱获取新知识的感觉，几乎把整天的时间都投入到学习中。她最喜欢做的事情，就是待在家附近的图书馆里流连忘返。</Wolfein_BackstoryChild_10.description>
  <!-- EN: Wolfein diligent child -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryChild_10.title>沃芬族 勤学的孩子</Wolfein_BackstoryChild_10.title>
  <!-- EN: diligent child -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryChild_10.titleShort>勤学的孩子</Wolfein_BackstoryChild_10.titleShort>
  
  <!-- EN: [PAWN_nameDef] is highly motivated when it comes to her studies. Her diligence has earned the admiration of adults. At school, she excels academically and maintains strong, positive relationships with her peers. -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryChild_11.description>[PAWN_nameDef]在学习方面非常上进，勤奋刻苦，深受长辈喜爱。她在学校成绩优异，与朋友之间也维持着良好的关系。</Wolfein_BackstoryChild_11.description>
  <!-- EN: Wolfein top student -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryChild_11.title>沃芬族 优等生</Wolfein_BackstoryChild_11.title>
  <!-- EN: top student -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryChild_11.titleShort>优等生</Wolfein_BackstoryChild_11.titleShort>
  
  <!-- EN: [PAWN_nameDef] is quite lazy by nature. She dislikes going out or exercising, preferring instead to spend her days at home playing games and reading comics. Her grades at school are mediocre at best, much to the frustration of her parents. -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryChild_12.description>[PAWN_nameDef]性格懒散，不爱运动，也不喜欢出门。她更愿意整天窝在家里打游戏、看漫画。她在学校的成绩也普普通通，这让她的父母感到颇为无奈。</Wolfein_BackstoryChild_12.description>
  <!-- EN: Wolfein lazy child -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryChild_12.title>沃芬族 懒惰的孩子</Wolfein_BackstoryChild_12.title>
  <!-- EN: lazy child -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryChild_12.titleShort>懒惰的孩子</Wolfein_BackstoryChild_12.titleShort>
  
  <!-- EN: From a young age, [PAWN_nameDef] demonstrated intelligence far beyond her peers, showing exceptional talent across multiple fields. However, her naturally frail body made it difficult for her to take part in physical activities or play with other children her age. -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryChild_13.description>[PAWN_nameDef]从小就展现出远超常人的智慧，在多个领域都展现出非凡的天赋。然而，[PAWN_nameDef]的体质天生较为虚弱，无法像其他同龄人那样参与运动或户外游戏。</Wolfein_BackstoryChild_13.description>
  <!-- EN: Wolfein genius -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryChild_13.title>沃芬族 天才儿童</Wolfein_BackstoryChild_13.title>
  <!-- EN: genius -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryChild_13.titleShort>天才儿童</Wolfein_BackstoryChild_13.titleShort>
  
  <!-- EN: [PAWN_nameDef]'s parents left when she was still very young due to work-related reasons, and she spent her childhood in the care of her grandparents. Her memories of her parents are faint, yet she has always quietly longed for the day she might see them again. -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryChild_14.description>[PAWN_nameDef]的父母在她年幼时因工作原因离开了她，她的童年是在祖父母的陪伴下度过的。对父母的记忆，她所剩无几，但内心始终怀着希望，盼望着有朝一日能再见到他们。</Wolfein_BackstoryChild_14.description>
  <!-- EN: Wolfein left-behind child -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryChild_14.title>沃芬族 留守儿童</Wolfein_BackstoryChild_14.title>
  <!-- EN: left-behind child -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryChild_14.titleShort>留守儿童</Wolfein_BackstoryChild_14.titleShort>
  
  <!-- EN: [PAWN_nameDef] received her education in a nation governed by another racial faction. Growing up in a diverse and multicultural environment broadened her perspective far beyond that of most others. -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryChild_15.description>[PAWN_nameDef]从小就在其他种族派系的国家接受教育，在多元文化的环境中成长与学习，使她的眼界远比常人开阔。</Wolfein_BackstoryChild_15.description>
  <!-- EN: Wolfein overseas student -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryChild_15.title>沃芬族 留学生</Wolfein_BackstoryChild_15.title>
  <!-- EN: overseas student -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryChild_15.titleShort>留学生</Wolfein_BackstoryChild_15.titleShort>
  
  <!-- EN: [PAWN_nameDef] has always been somewhat reclusive since childhood. For reasons unknown, people around her seemed to keep their distance, intentionally or not. But [PAWN_nameDef] never minded—she found greater comfort in solitude than in company. -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryChild_16.description>[PAWN_nameDef]从小性格就较为孤僻，不知为何，身边的人似乎总是有意无意地疏远她。不过对此，[PAWN_nameDef]并不在意，反而更享受一个人独处的安静时光。</Wolfein_BackstoryChild_16.description>
  <!-- EN: Wolfein lonely child -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryChild_16.title>沃芬族 孤僻的孩子</Wolfein_BackstoryChild_16.title>
  <!-- EN: lonely child -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryChild_16.titleShort>孤僻的孩子</Wolfein_BackstoryChild_16.titleShort>
  
  <!-- EN: [PAWN_nameDef]'s family lived in deep poverty, and her childhood was marked by hardship. Her parents worked late into the night every day, leaving [PAWN_nameDef] to take care of herself. As a result, she matured far earlier than most children her age. -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryChild_17.description>[PAWN_nameDef]的家庭十分贫困，她的童年也因此格外艰辛。父母每天工作到深夜才回家，[PAWN_nameDef]平时只能独自照顾自己，这也让她比同龄人更加早熟懂事。</Wolfein_BackstoryChild_17.description>
  <!-- EN: Wolfein poor child -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryChild_17.title>沃芬族 贫穷的孩子</Wolfein_BackstoryChild_17.title>
  <!-- EN: poor child -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryChild_17.titleShort>贫穷的孩子</Wolfein_BackstoryChild_17.titleShort>
  
  <!-- EN: From an early age, [PAWN_nameDef] showed an exceptional talent for the arts, with a deep passion for drawing. She often spent her class time sketching in secret, which led to her falling behind academically. -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryChild_18.description>[PAWN_nameDef]从小便展现出非凡的艺术天赋，尤其热爱绘画。她经常在上课时偷偷作画，以至于学业成绩并不出色。</Wolfein_BackstoryChild_18.description>
  <!-- EN: Wolfein little painter -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryChild_18.title>沃芬族 小画家</Wolfein_BackstoryChild_18.title>
  <!-- EN: little painter -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryChild_18.titleShort>小画家</Wolfein_BackstoryChild_18.titleShort>
  
  <!-- EN: [PAWN_nameDef] has a strong passion for sports. She joined the school’s track and field club and actively took part in numerous athletic competitions. Her exceptional physical abilities earned her many awards and widespread recognition. -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryChild_19.description>[PAWN_nameDef]热爱运动，加入了学校的田径社团，并积极参与各类大小型比赛。凭借出色的运动能力，[PAWN_nameDef]赢得了许多奖项，备受瞩目。</Wolfein_BackstoryChild_19.description>
  <!-- EN: Wolfein little athlete -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryChild_19.title>沃芬族 小运动员</Wolfein_BackstoryChild_19.title>
  <!-- EN: little athlete -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryChild_19.titleShort>小运动员</Wolfein_BackstoryChild_19.titleShort>
  
  <!-- EN: [PAWN_nameDef] has always had a strong interest in cooking. She not only enjoys good food but also finds great satisfaction in preparing it herself. [PAWN_nameDef] dreams of becoming an outstanding chef in the future. -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryChild_20.description>[PAWN_nameDef]从小就对烹饪充满兴趣，她不仅热爱享受美食，更喜欢亲手制作佳肴时带来的满足与成就感。[PAWN_nameDef]梦想着有一天能成为一名出色的厨师。</Wolfein_BackstoryChild_20.description>
  <!-- EN: Wolfein little chef -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryChild_20.title>沃芬族 小厨师</Wolfein_BackstoryChild_20.title>
  <!-- EN: little chef -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryChild_20.titleShort>小厨师</Wolfein_BackstoryChild_20.titleShort>
  
  <!-- EN: [PAWN_nameDef] enjoys tinkering with small machines and crafting various handmade items. Her creations are always clever and full of personality, and her friends absolutely adore the handcrafted gifts she makes for them. -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryChild_21.description>[PAWN_nameDef]喜欢摆弄小机械，也热衷于制作各种手工小物。她亲手制作的工艺品总是别具匠心，深受朋友们喜爱，大家对她的手工作品总是爱不释手。</Wolfein_BackstoryChild_21.description>
  <!-- EN: Wolfein little artisan -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryChild_21.title>沃芬族 小工匠</Wolfein_BackstoryChild_21.title>
  <!-- EN: little artisan -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryChild_21.titleShort>小工匠</Wolfein_BackstoryChild_21.titleShort>
  
  <!-- EN: [PAWN_nameDef]'s family runs a restaurant, and in her spare time, she helps out with tasks she can manage. The customers are fond of this hardworking girl and often give her small tips as pocket money, which always brings her great joy. -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryChild_22.description>[PAWN_nameDef]的家庭经营着一家餐厅，闲暇时她常会帮家里做些力所能及的事情。顾客们也很喜欢这个勤快的孩子，经常会给她一些小费当作零花钱，这让[PAWN_nameDef]感到格外开心。</Wolfein_BackstoryChild_22.description>
  <!-- EN: Wolfein little artisan -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryChild_22.title>沃芬族 小服务员</Wolfein_BackstoryChild_22.title>
  <!-- EN: little artisan -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryChild_22.titleShort>小服务员</Wolfein_BackstoryChild_22.titleShort>
  
  <!-- EN: [PAWN_nameDef] has a deep love for nature. Her favorite pastime is visiting the botanical garden near her home. There, she learned some basic gardening skills and began growing a few charming little plants at home. -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryChild_23.description>[PAWN_nameDef]非常热爱大自然，她最喜欢做的事就是前往家附近的植物园散步。在那里，[PAWN_nameDef]学到了一些关于植物栽培的知识，并在家中尝试种植了几株可爱的植物。</Wolfein_BackstoryChild_23.description>
  <!-- EN: Wolfein little gardener -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryChild_23.title>沃芬族 小园丁</Wolfein_BackstoryChild_23.title>
  <!-- EN: little gardener -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryChild_23.titleShort>小园丁</Wolfein_BackstoryChild_23.titleShort>
  
  <!-- EN: [PAWN_nameDef] has loved music since childhood. After learning some basic music theory, she often played simple instruments with friends from the school music club, losing herself in the joyful world of melodies and rhythm. -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryChild_24.description>[PAWN_nameDef]从小就热爱音乐。在学习了一些基础乐理知识后，[PAWN_nameDef]经常与音乐社团的小伙伴们一起，用简单的乐器演奏乐曲，沉浸在音乐的海洋中，乐在其中。</Wolfein_BackstoryChild_24.description>
  <!-- EN: Wolfein little gardener -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryChild_24.title>沃芬族 小音乐家</Wolfein_BackstoryChild_24.title>
  <!-- EN: little gardener -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryChild_24.titleShort>小音乐家</Wolfein_BackstoryChild_24.titleShort>
  
  <!-- EN: Due to a lack of proper guidance at home, [PAWN_nameDef] developed a habit of bullying her peers from a young age. She often took other children's snacks and toys for herself, much to the frustration of both her teachers and parents. -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryChild_25.description>由于家庭教育上的缺失，[PAWN_nameDef]从小便养成了欺负同龄人的坏习惯。她常常强占其他孩子的零食和玩具，令老师和父母都十分头疼。</Wolfein_BackstoryChild_25.description>
  <!-- EN: Wolfein little bully -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryChild_25.title>沃芬族 小恶霸</Wolfein_BackstoryChild_25.title>
  <!-- EN: little bully -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryChild_25.titleShort>小恶霸</Wolfein_BackstoryChild_25.titleShort>
  
  <!-- EN: [PAWN_nameDef] has always had a deep affection for animals. She pleaded with her parents many times to let her keep a pet at home, but due to financial or living conditions, her wish never came true. Still, [PAWN_nameDef] hopes that one day, when she's grown up, she can have a few animals to keep her company. -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryChild_26.description>[PAWN_nameDef]特别喜爱小动物，多次恳求父母允许在家中饲养宠物。可惜由于家庭条件的限制，这个愿望一直未能实现。[PAWN_nameDef]一直希望等自己长大后，能够养几只动物来陪伴自己。</Wolfein_BackstoryChild_26.description>
  <!-- EN: Wolfein friend of animals -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryChild_26.title>沃芬族 动物之友</Wolfein_BackstoryChild_26.title>
  <!-- EN: friend of animals -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryChild_26.titleShort>动物之友</Wolfein_BackstoryChild_26.titleShort>
  
  <!-- EN: [PAWN_nameDef] is a kind and gentle child. Whenever her friends are in trouble, she’s always the first to offer help. Her warm and sincere nature gradually won the hearts of those around her, and she began making more and more friends. -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryChild_27.description>[PAWN_nameDef]是个温柔善良的孩子。每当伙伴遇到困难时，[PAWN_nameDef]总是第一个伸出援手。她的友善与真诚逐渐打动了身边的人，也因此结交了越来越多的朋友。</Wolfein_BackstoryChild_27.description>
  <!-- EN: Wolfein kind child -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryChild_27.title>沃芬族 善良的孩子</Wolfein_BackstoryChild_27.title>
  <!-- EN: kind child -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryChild_27.titleShort>善良的孩子</Wolfein_BackstoryChild_27.titleShort>
  
  <!-- EN: [PAWN_nameDef] comes from a very wealthy family, living a life of comfort and abundance. All household chores are taken care of by the servants, and for [PAWN_nameDef], life is simply about enjoying its luxuries. -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryChild_28.description>[PAWN_nameDef]的家庭十分富有，她从小衣食无忧，生活无比优渥。家中的大小事务都由仆人打理，[PAWN_nameDef]只需安心享受生活带来的舒适与便利。</Wolfein_BackstoryChild_28.description>
  <!-- EN: Wolfein richer child -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryChild_28.title>沃芬族 富人家的孩子</Wolfein_BackstoryChild_28.title>
  <!-- EN: richer child -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryChild_28.titleShort>富人家的孩子</Wolfein_BackstoryChild_28.titleShort>
  
  <!-- EN: [PAWN_nameDef] had always been fascinated by the idea of joining the scouts. One day, by a stroke of luck, her wish came true. During her time with the scouts, [PAWN_nameDef] learned many useful survival skills, such as foraging for food in the wild, setting up camp, and identifying different types of plants. -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryChild_29.description>[PAWN_nameDef]一直对童子军生活充满向往。在一次偶然的机会下，她终于实现了这个愿望。加入童子军后，[PAWN_nameDef]学会了许多实用技能，比如在野外寻找食物、搭建营地，以及辨识各种植物等生存知识。</Wolfein_BackstoryChild_29.description>
  <!-- EN: Wolfein scout -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryChild_29.title>沃芬族 童子军</Wolfein_BackstoryChild_29.title>
  <!-- EN: scout -->
  <Wolfein_BackstoryChild_29.titleShort>童子军</Wolfein_BackstoryChild_29.titleShort>
  
